name: ImageOcrData
description: Represents data obtained by OCR (optical character recognition) of an image

properties.name: ocrText
properties.description: Represents the text obtained by OCR of the image

properties.name: ocrLanguageId
properties.description: Represents the OCR language, with values such as EN-US

methods.name: load
methods.description: Fills the proxy object created in JavaScript layer with property and object values specified in the parameter.

parameters.name: param
parameters.description: Accepts parameter and relationship names as delimited string or an array. Or, provide [loadOption](loadoption.md) object.
